thewikipedialibrary-desc: Sseɛlem imseqdac ɣer uqbal i ttwaqeblen deg temkarḍit n Wikipedia mi ara yaweḍ umṣiḍan-nsen leḥsab n yibeddilen i ilaqen akked mi ara temmed tmeddurt n umiḍan-nsen.
notification-header-twl-eligiblity: Gidha ! Tettwaqebleḍ ɣer temkarḍit n Wikipedia, tzemṛeḍ ad tkecmeḍ tura ɣer-s.
